item.title: Zava x Manjaya
item.description: This pairing was between our F1 female from WC Arlo x Perregrin/Pyro’s daughter, and our male from Kammerflage Kreations, Zava. Zava was a vibrant rainbow Ambilobe. His yellow sat on top of a bright red dermal layer, and his bars were deep royal blue. F1 Manjaya brings fresh genetics and a chance at that Perregrin/Sparkles yellow. Hatch dates 7/27/22 - 8/21/2022 Hatch rate 8/14 F1 F2 F3 M1 M2
